{"tid":472033,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣先叫成熟","createTime":"2017-11-17T22:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-18T09:42:11.000Z","uid":137315,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ff8913718ecb445f1dd15d53a167c2b8b32c59d8","tid":472033,"uid":137315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T22:50:07.000Z","msg":"硬係覺得自己唔夠成熟<br />\n唔夠好 根本唔會有人鍾意<br />\n唔想比人覺得自己好幼稚"},{"pid":"b109e6520e39e959a47b7b7d9db0baa67366ea26","tid":472033,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:06:42.000Z","msg":"做之前諗過計過"},{"pid":"bf7add0315660323ac9bebef3d18a58b6081ee3f","tid":472033,"uid":8129,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:20:25.000Z","msg":"煮到3成熟就夠"},{"pid":"cf0d5240f841bd6174a222256164a148ea37944a","tid":472033,"uid":136502,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T23:40:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>硬係覺得自己唔夠成熟<br />\n唔夠好 根本唔會有人鍾意<br />\n唔想比人覺得自己好幼稚</blockquote><br />\n同樓主一樣覺得自己唔成熟<br />\n不斷逼自己成熟但又冇定義到成熟究竟係咩<br />\n所以到最後 我定義咗佢為 唔鍾意做嘅事亦能夠一一去做<br />\n辛苦嘅事亦一一捱過<br />\n不哭<br />\n不鬧<br />\n不發脾氣<br />\n俾人攞著數亦有大人之心不記仇<br />\n然後去專注事業<br />\n<br />\n我會唔會認真咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f550b2995718558a1a949fdeefa02c1e4036667","tid":472033,"uid":16871,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:29:50.000Z","msg":"標準答案 唔再諗點樣先叫成熟"},{"pid":"f39dd65a7003f4be492492514182d15481f24d61","tid":472033,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:40:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0d4ccae870b5ca2dadec2aee2bf6af27412ce12f","tid":472033,"uid":28163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:43:02.000Z","msg":"Rich"},{"pid":"16774c88f5397af086169a3046315339f76a33d4","tid":472033,"uid":37414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:44:03.000Z","msg":"有諗係唔係就代表仲未係"},{"pid":"0dc9b225d792e234cba82e2e8c9180368cc26d54","tid":472033,"uid":10845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:44:24.000Z","msg":"你鍾意嘅人鍾意你嗰陣時咪叫成熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢唔鍾意你咪話鳩你幼稚唔成熟囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n抽象野黎嘅，唔洗太介懷"},{"pid":"205659f3f485a9f2aaab0308b212b154a0c3783b","tid":472033,"uid":52816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:46:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6c392a4feb38f5f1ff962761c2a6902cb135857c","tid":472033,"uid":36329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:47:35.000Z","msg":"你為咗討好人而變成熟已經唔係成熟啦<br />\n樓主可以諗返以前嘅事<br />\n睇下有冇咩時候應該認真對待某啲事但冇做到<br />\n有冇咩時候可以有更好嘅處理方法但冇做到<br />\n下次唔好再重蹈覆轍"},{"pid":"67319c57ed81e7f7c6a81a1e99fda9abcb72242b","tid":472033,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T00:48:06.000Z","msg":"十成熟"},{"pid":"48350c25dc4c02a3fd87e5b9797e96ab887adcaa","tid":472033,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T09:36:04.000Z","msg":"無首先你個樣要夠成熟<br />\n呃得下人"},{"pid":"ee7a489f2843c75783d169a3e8660ff14b3ea39f","tid":472033,"uid":68641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T09:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>標準答案 唔再諗點樣先叫成熟</blockquote><br />\nFair point"}]}